title: #261 Ruined Hang
description:
Hey post-Labor Day Tuesgays, it's a great ep as Mark & Joe meet a woman who loves Mark's personality, Joe gets mistaken for a college student by a crazy guy, and Mark upsets yet another morning radio host. Check it out!
